  • Constructor Details

    • Board

      public Board​(java.lang.String[] nicknames)
      The board is the memory of the game. It will contains all the cells of the board, all the players and all the workers It has to be initialized only when the order of player will be established by the birthday. playerInGame, that represents the player that is now playing, will be initialized as Player1
      Parameters:
      nicknames - the nickname of the players
